rows.label: tlk000501_07_msg0001
rows.name:
Nilny now standing in for time
being as Acting Chairman.

rows.label: tlk000501_07_msg0002
rows.name:
Nilny swear to change the way
things work around here, undo
Bahn's influence.

rows.label: tlk000501_07_msg0003
rows.name:
First we crack down on slackers and
shady dealings. Want Avaritia to be
known for clean, honest trade.

rows.label: tlk000501_07_msg0004
rows.name:
Yes, Nilny looking forward to bright
future of Avaritia Trade Guild!
